text: The Summer Youth Olympic Games or the Games of the Olympiad == List of modern Summer Youth Olympic Games == * 2010 - Games of the I Olympiad - Singapore * 2014 - Games of the II Olympiad - Nanjing, China * 2018 - Games of the III Olympiad - Buenos Aires, Argentina * 2026 - Games of the IV Olympiad - Dakar, Senegal * 2030 - Games of the V Olympiad - unknown
title: Summer Youth Olympic Games
